caption:
Founded in 1880, REGAL Shoe & Co. has played a defining role in Japanese footwear—introducing Goodyear welt construction and building a legacy of meticulous craftsmanship.

That same philosophy informs our collaboration, brought to life in REGAL Shoe & Co.’s factory in Kashiwa, Chiba.

Each step—from cutting and lasting to final finishing—reflects a shared commitment to material integrity and enduring design.

Available Friday, May 30th online and in stores.

Preview the collaboration now via the link in bio.
